title: Pucko, parody of Jackass (Homemade)
description:
A parody (made by a couple of my friends) of the hugely famous show Jackass. Or well, that\&#039;s what they called it, anyway. The first couple of seconds contain a couple of lines in Swedish, but the rest is purely random things, as well as some jokes you might not get because you don\&#039;t know us. 

On a final note, the clips were shot a couple of years back. And some parts of it are pretty lame... Anyway. If you\&#039;re sitting there, having nothing better to do, just download it and watch it. It\&#039;ll only kill some time, braincells and possibly your grandma, but hey, sacrifices must be made, right? :P

Enjoy. Or well... Watch.
